Package: extrememix
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Estimation of Extreme Value Mixture Models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-06-21
Author: Manuele Leonelli
Maintainer: Manuele Leonelli <manuele.leonelli@ie.edu>
Description: Fits extreme value mixture models, which are models for tails not requiring selection of a threshold, for continuous data. It includes functions for model comparison, estimation of quantity of interest in extreme value analysis and plotting. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: 
   evd, ggplot2, gridExtra, mixtools, Rcpp, threshr, RcppProgress
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppProgress
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/manueleleonelli/extrememix
